text: Mutton steak was very unappetising. Its suppose to be red not orangey. It taste sweet and full of scrambled egg. Too eggy. The packaging is not nice as well put in container instead of styrofoam. This place the only good thing is the prata. The rest is so bad.
Prata is quite good. Fluffy and fragrant. Fish curry is not spicy and tastes good. Can drink the curry kind. $3.60 for 2 egg.
Very messy team, no place to take a proper order and no they will forget your order after taking it. Ordered the mutton steak and it was very unappetising. The soup kambing and Prata salvaged though
very good food, affordable, big portions,
Good 24 hr option. Prata crispy and made to order
